text: Luján Partido is a partido in the northeastern part of Buenos Aires Province in Argentina. The provincial subdivision has a population of about 94,000 inhabitants in an area of , and its capital city is Luján, which is from Buenos Aires. ==Economy== The economy of Luján Partido is dominated by farming, other aspects include textile and medical manufacturing, and the production of agrochemicals and agricultural machinery. ==Settlements== *Cortínez *Jáuregui *Luján *Olivera *Open Door *Carlos Keen *Pueblo Nuevo *Torres ==External links== * Luján Argentina Website * Luján net website * InfoBAN Luján Category:Partidos of Buenos Aires Province Category:States and territories established in 1731
